<h3>NAP Consistency</h3>
<p>Your Name, Address, and Phone Number must match exactly across every listing. If your GBP says "123 Main St, Suite 4," every other listing must say the same. Not "123 Main Street #4."</p>
<p>Inconsistent NAP confuses Google and hurts local rankings. Audit all listings quarterly.</p>
